Mr_Eazi_Property_Ft_Mo-T Photo Fastdownload On this new record, watch Mr Eazi take it to a new level as he features South African trumpeter, Mo-T of the Mi Casa band. The singer Mr Eazi revealed more on the tracks origins in an interview with Ebro of Apple’s Beats 1, where during the studio sessions he played around with the word “Property” and was able to come up with a freestyle while it was being recorded by the studio producer and hence the birth of the song “Property”. Mr Eazi in this video plays the role of a lover willing to give it all for his love interest while in this modern day not many “lovers” would do that, he tells and shows his exceptional love story here. Watch and Enjoy.  